data.description: Experience lakeside living at its finest with this beautiful Lake Dow home! Your private backyard is just steps away from the tranquil lake. Enjoy the beauty of of nature on the deck off of the main level. The four-sided brick residence features a fully finished basement, and the main floor hosts the master bedroom. Enjoy beautiful floors throughout the main level, tiled bathrooms, and a total of five bedrooms with 3.5 bathrooms. The open kitchen features an island breakfast bar, granite countertops, abundant cabinets, a breakfast room, and a cozy keeping room complete with a fireplace. Upstairs, discover three bedrooms, while the basement includes a generous bedroom, a family room with a built-in bar or potential kitchen for an in-law suite, two offices, and ample storage. Don't forget the added bonus of being in the sought-after Ola school district! Call now to make an appointment. Please allow 24-hr notice.
